      <div class="location-section">
        <h3>Our location</h3>
        <p>We are located in a small haven of peace less than 5 minutes from 2 accesses to the A12 motorway (Fribourg-Nord and Fribourg-Sud) and only 1 kilometer from a well-served railway station (Belfaux-Village, a few minutes from Fribourg station) giving access to the major Swiss cities (Geneva, Zürich, Basel) in less than 1h30.</p>

        <p>This studio and parking space are in a well-located village near the city of Fribourg. If you travel by train, "Belfaux-Village" train station is less than 1 km. This train station has trains every 30 minutes to Fribourg city centre (4 minutes train ride), which is then well connected to other major cities of Switzerland (Bern is at 20 minutes, Geneva at 1h30m, Zurich at 1h30m, Basel at 1h30m).</p>

        <p>If you have or rent a car, the flat is less than 5 minutes from 2 highway entrances ("Fribourg-Nord" and "Fribourg-Sud").</p>
      </div>

